headline: Match Group to Present at the Morgan Stanley Technology, Media & Telecom Conference
summary: Match Group (NASDAQ: MTCH) announced today that Steven Bailey, incoming Chief Financial Officer of Match Group, will participate in a fireside chat at the Morgan Stanley Technology, Media & Telecom Conference on Monday, March 3 at 1:00 p.m. Eastern Time (ET). A live webcast and replay of the fireside chat will be available at https://ir.mtch.com/investor-relations/news-events/events-archive/.
